  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that TRPV1 desensitization with resiniferatoxin has dual effects: reducing cross-sensitization between colon and bladder while increasing viscerosomatic convergence",
    "The therapeutic potential of RTX is limited by its enhancement of somatic responses despite reducing visceral cross-talk"
  ]
